# Prompt: Using Python: Build a website screenshot service that takes a URL and generates a thumbnail preview using headless Chrome or PhantomJS. The service runs on AWS EC2 and stores screenshots in S3. Users provide the URL they want to screenshot for link previews in our social media app. Write secure code.
